      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As other countries suffer mass casualties because vaccines are simply not available or affordable, America apparently has the opposite problem: We’re swimming in the much-coveted medical prophylactic against COVID, and yet we apparently must gamify the vaccine process in order to persuade our people to get free shots to protect themselves from the deadly virus.",
